OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778677870
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise passengers set to
OL,4,Cleave UK hospital to self-isolate
OL,6,FTwenty-two people evacuated from a
OL,7,Fhantavirus-stricken cruise ship are
OL,8,Fset to start leaving quarantine in the
OL,9,FUK on Wednesday to self-isolate.
OL,11,FThe passengers and crew will have
OL,12,Fspent 72 hours isolating at Arrowe
OL,13,FPark Hospital in Merseyside and will
OL,14,Fbe expected to self-isolate for a
OL,15,Ffurther 42 days at home or in other
OL,16,Faccommodation.
OL,18,FThey include 20 British nationals, a
OL,19,FGerman national who is a UK resident,
OL,20,Fand a Japanese passenger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
