OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778677870
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise passengers set to
OL,4,Cleave UK hospital to self-isolate
OL,6,FTen other passengers from the UK
OL,7,Foverseas territories of St Helena and
OL,8,FAscension Island are being "brought to
OL,9,Fthe UK to complete their self-
OL,10,Fisolation as a precautionary measure",
OL,11,Fthe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FOfficials said these people had been
OL,15,Fin contact with those affected by the
OL,16,Foutbreak and that none of them is
OL,17,Fcurrently symptomatic.
OL,26,@pD@\OUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778677870
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise passengers set to
OL,4,Cleave UK hospital to self-isolate
OL,6,FThe UKHSA said the relocation is "of
OL,7,Fsome contacts who are already
OL,8,Fisolating, to places where they can
OL,9,Fsafely self-isolate with access to
OL,10,Fappropriate specialist medical
OL,11,Fservices".
OL,13,F"This is because England's NHS high-
OL,14,Fconsequence infectious disease network
OL,15,Fis well equipped to respond if they
OL,16,Fbecome unwell," the agency added.
OL,26,@nD@bOUsD@IO]uD@AOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778677870
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise passengers set to
OL,4,Cleave UK hospital to self-isolate
OL,6,F"Currently, none of these contacts are
OL,7,Fsymptomatic and this is precautionary
OL,8,Fto support communities in UK overseas
OL,9,Fterritories. We will set out where
OL,10,Fthey will isolate in due course."
OL,12,FAll of the passengers of the
OL,13,Fhantavirus-stricken MV Hondius cruise
OL,14,Fship had disembarked and left Tenerife
OL,15,Fearlier on Tuesday, with flights to
OL,16,Fmore than 20 countries and dozens in
OL,17,Fquarantine.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
