OL,3,CHantavirus cruise passengers set to
OL,4,Cleave UK hospital to self-isolate
OL,6,FA French woman became the latest to be
OL,7,Fconfirmed as infected, while an
OL,8,FAmerican was suspected of infection
OL,9,Fafter initial testing.
OL,11,FPassengers began flying home aboard
OL,12,Fmilitary and government planes on
OL,13,FSunday after the MV Hondius anchored
OL,14,Fin the Canary Islands.
OL,16,FPersonnel in full-body protective gear
OL,17,Fand breathing masks escorted the
OL,18,Ftravellers from the ship to shore in
OL,19,FTenerife and onto an airport, with the
OL,20,Ffinal flight departing on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778677870
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise passengers set to
OL,4,Cleave UK hospital to self-isolate
OL,6,F"If they stayed longer on the ship,
OL,7,Fthe situation could have been
OL,8,Fdifficult," said Tedros Adhanom
OL,9,FGhebreyesus, director-general of the
OL,10,FWorld Health Organization.
OL,12,FHe said citizens of the countries that
OL,13,Fpassengers are returning to should
OL,14,Fknow "there is nothing to fear, the
OL,15,Frisk is low, this is not another
OL,16,FCovid."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
