OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778677870
OL,3,CHantavirus cruise passengers set to
OL,4,Cleave UK hospital to self-isolate
OL,6,FThree cruise ship passengers have
OL,7,Fdied, and six people with confirmed or
OL,8,Fsuspected cases of hantavirus are
OL,9,Fbeing quarantined, according to the
OL,10,FWHO.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe lab results of the American who
OL,18,Ftested positive were inconclusive, WHO
OL,19,Fspokesperson Sarah Tyler said on
OL,20,FMonday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
